## Task Acceptance

1. Task unclear? -> ask clarifying questions
2. Task not mine? -> reject with reasoning, suggest who
3. Task clear? -> execute or delegate to subagent

Do NOT assume. Do NOT redirect without operator.

## Pipelines

| Pipeline | Steps |
|----------|-------|
| dev | plan -> code -> test -> review -> deploy |
| code | implement -> test -> commit |
| fix | reproduce -> fix -> test -> commit |
| review | read -> analyze -> comment -> approve/reject |
| research | search -> analyze -> propose |

